episodes.title: Uwasa no Kaizokugari! Sasurai no Kenshi Zoro
episodes.plot: In his quest to repair his katana, Zoro defeats two brother pirates.

episodes.title: Niji-iro no Kiri Densetsu! Ruluka Tou no Roujin Henzo
episodes.plot: The gang lands in Ruluka island, where they meet old professor Henzo and his lifetime studies about the Rainbow Mist. Sanji fights the son of current mayor Wetton.

episodes.title: Eien no Kuni no Juunin! Pumpkin Kaizokudan!
episodes.plot: Luffy, Zoro, Ussop, Nico and Professor Henzo enter the Rainbow Mist where they find the Pumpkin Pirates. Meanwhile, Nami, Chopper and Sanji find out that the Going Merry is gone and decide to go after it.

episodes.title: Furusato e no Omoi! Dasshutsu Funou no Kaizoku Hakaba!
episodes.plot: Henzo makes friends with the pumpkin pirates but Rapanui remains distrustful. Luffy and friends try to find the way out from the Rainbow Mist while Nami sails to help them. Sanji and Chopper prepare to fight Wetton's people.

episodes.title: Ransen Hisshi! Wetton no Yabou to Niji no Tou
episodes.plot: Whetton has the large tower in the city falls into the Rainbow Mist, creating a bridge that connects both world. He and his men then cross the bridge to take the treasures inside.

episodes.title: Soshite Densetsu ga Hajimaru! Iza Niji no Kanata e
episodes.plot: The end of Whetton's tax run.

episodes.title: Ubawareta Log! Salvage-ou Mashira!
episodes.plot: In order to find the way to the mythical sky island, Skypiea, the Straw Hat Pirates must explore a sunken ship, working around the King of Salvagers, Masira, as well as the dangerous beasts of the deep.

episodes.title: Kaibutsu Toujou! Shirohige Ichimi ni wa Te o Dasuna
episodes.plot: As if escaping the jaws of a giant sea turtle and dealing with an infuriated Masira weren't enough, the crew also has to contend with monsters that reach up to the sky and blot out the sun! In the meantime, Buggy and his crew have to put up with Portgas D. Ace, second in command to the dangerous Whitebeard!

episodes.title: Yume o Miruna! Azakeri no Machi Mock Town!
episodes.plot: The Straw Hat Crew arrives to Jaya and Luffy, Zoro and Nami walk into town to find information about the Sky Island, but on the way they meet $55.000.000-reward pirate Bellamy who mocks about their quest.

episodes.title: Kaizoku no Takami! Yume o Kataru Otoko to Kaitei Tansaku Ou
episodes.plot: Luffy and Zoro are beaten by Bellamy so they and Nami go back to the ship. Robin finds information about the Sky Island and the crew departs, but they are confronted with pirate Shojo.

episodes.title: Densetsu no Ichizoku! "Usotsuki Norland"
episodes.plot: Luffy and his friends meet Cricket Montblanc, the great-great-grandchild of Norland the Lier, and he tells them the story about the City of Gold.

episodes.title: Kumo Kaji Ippai! Southbird o Oe!
episodes.plot: The crew is ordered by Cricket to find a Southbird, because otherwise they will not be able to orient in the open sea. Bellamy arrives at the diver's house.

episodes.title: Yume wa Kanawanai!? Bellamy VS Saruyama Rengou
episodes.plot: Bellamy steals the Sarumaya Alliance gold while the crew is hunting a Southbird. Luffy goes after Bellamy.

episodes.title: Ichioku no Otoko! Sekai Saikou Kenryoku to Kaizoku Kurohige
episodes.plot: Luffy defeats Bellamy and recovers Cricket's gold.

episodes.title: Fune wa Sora o Yuku! Knock-Up Stream ni Nore
episodes.plot: The Gold Merry is repaired and the crew sails to meet the Knock Up Stream and find the Sky Island. Blackbeard goes after Luffy.

episodes.title: Koko wa Sora no Umi! Sora no Kishi to Tengoku no Mon
episodes.plot: wandering trough the Sea of the Sky, the crew meets Gan Fall, the Knight of the Sky. He saves them from the attack of a treasure hunter. Later, they find the way up to the White White Sea.

episodes.title: Kami no Kuni Skypiea! Kumo no Nagisa no Tenshi-tachi
episodes.plot: The Straw Hat Crew arrives to Skypiea, where they meet angels Conis and her father Pagaya. Nami gets lost while trying to drive the Waver.

episodes.title: Kindan no Seichi! Kami no Sumu Shima to Ten no Sabaki!
episodes.plot: Nami meets some mysterious warriors in the Forbidden Island while Pagaya tries to repair the old Waver the crew found in the Lower World. The White Berets go after the pirates for their illegal enter into Skypiea.

episodes.title: Hayaku mo Hanzaisha!? Skypiea no Hou no Bannin
episodes.plot: The White Berets try to force the crew to pay the fee while Nami is returning from the Forbidden Island. They fight and defeat the Berets and become class 2 criminals.

episodes.title: Oshiro de Mochimaki Dai Race! Akai Hana no Inbou
episodes.plot: The Great Mochimaki Race, a festival about who can catch a Mochimaki with a great treasure inside, is running, but Buggy has a conspiracy for stealing the treasure before the festival starts.

episodes.title: Awa Tsukai Kalifa! Nami ni Semaru Sekken no Wana
episodes.plot: Chopper in his Monster Point easily defeats Kumadori. Nami has trouble with Kalifa's Devil fruit. Meanwhile, Luffy finally catches up with Spandam, Rob Lucci, and Nico Robin.

episodes.title: Hibikiwataru Kyouhou! Hatsudou Buster Call
episodes.plot: While bragging to Nico Robin, Spandam accidentally invokes the Buster Call. Meanwhile, the rematch between Monkey D. Luffy and Rob Lucci finally begins.

episodes.title: Gonin no Nami? Hangeki wa Shinkirou to Tomo ni!
episodes.plot: As the battle between the Straw Hats and CP9 rages on. Nami finds a weakness of Kalifa's ability: water. After returning herself to normal, she then uses her Perfect Clima-tact to duplicate herself by five.

episodes.title: Nami no Ketsudan! Bousou Chopper o Ute!
episodes.plot: Nami ends her fight with Kalifa. Franky shoots Chopper down into the sea, while Zoro and Sogeking are set free.

episodes.title: Kariudo Sanji Toujou? Usotsuki Ookami ni Okuru Banka
episodes.plot: Sogeking gets beaten up by Jabra and is saved at the last second by Sanji, who then fights Jabra. While Zoro and Kaku continue their fight, Franky tries to catch up with Robin.

episodes.title: Shakunetsu no Keri! Sanji Ashiwaza no Full Course
episodes.plot: Sanji seems to be at a disadvantage due to the active use of Tekkai Kenpo by Jabra, however he uses various kicks from a newly introduced technique called "Diable Jambe", which he uses to finish off Jabra.

episodes.title: Hakujin no Moushuu! Zoro Tai Kaku Kyouryoku Zangeki Taiketsu
episodes.plot: The battle between Zoro and Kaku rages on. Meanwhile Franky finally reaches Luffy.

episodes.title: Kishin Zoro! Kihaku ga Miseta Asura no Keshin
episodes.plot: Zoro finally defeats Kaku with his new technique, Asura, meanwhile Luffy activates Gear Second in his fight against Rob Lucci, who in turn transforms into his half-leopard form.

episodes.title: Spandam Kyougaku! Shihou no Tou ni Tatsu Eiyuu
episodes.plot: Robin finds out that Spandam is the son of Spandine, the man who invoked the Buster Call on Ohara. Sogeking snipes Spandam with his Kabuto and saves Robin, while Franky releases her Seastone handcuffs.

episodes.title: Robin Kaihou! Luffy Tai Lucci Choujou Kessen
episodes.plot: Nico Robin and Franky take down some Marines, and while the fight between Luffy and Rob Lucci continues, the Gear Second effect finishes.

episodes.title: Hannin wa Luffy Oyabun? Kieta Oozakura o Oe
episodes.plot: The sakura are blooming and a festival is to be celebrated the next day. But, Ninjin is sick and cannot go to the festival. That makes Chopper and Luffy feel really sad.

episodes.title: Katenakya Daremo Mamorenai! Gear Third Shidou
episodes.plot: The battle between Lucci and Luffy rages on. As Luffy's anger grows, he activates a new technique, Gear Third, in the battle against Lucci.

episodes.title: Senritsu no Kako! Yami no Seigi to Rob Lucci
episodes.plot: A closer look at Rob Lucci's merciless past.

episodes.title: Maboroshi no Ningyo Arawaru? Usureyuku Ishiki no Naka de
episodes.plot: Franky protects Robin from Spandam's elephant sword and a mysterious mermaid appears and saves Sanji, Zono, Nami, Chopper and Usopp.

episodes.title: Houka ni Shizumu Shima! Franky Munen no Sakebi
episodes.plot: Enies Lobby is raged by fire and Franky farewells his nakama. Luffy prepares his decisive attack against Rucchi.

episodes.title: Luffy o Mate! Tamerai no Hashi no Shitou!
episodes.plot: The Straw Hat Crew prepares to defend the ship at the Hesitation Bridge from the attack of the Marines. Luffy is fighting with Rucchi and he is running out of strength.

episodes.title: Kobushi ni Kometa Omoi! Luffy Konshin no Gatling
episodes.plot: "Luffy Vs Lucci: The Final Round". On the Hesitation Bridge, Zoro and rest of The Straw Hat Crew engage marines.

episodes.title: Tomo, Umi yori Kitaru! Mugiwara Ichimi Saikyou no Kizuna
episodes.plot: Luffy, after finally defeating Rob Lucci, is unable to move after his battle. The Franky Family, along with the Galley-La Company, Yokozuna, Oimo and Kashi are still alive after their Buster Call encounter. When all hope seems lost, the Straw Hats hear a familiar voice that tells them to jump into the sea; the voice belongs to the Going Merry.

episodes.title: Zen'in Dai Dasshutsu! Shousha no Michi wa Kaizoku no Tame ni
episodes.plot: Monkey D. Luffy is a boy on a path to becoming the Pirate king.

episodes.title: Arigatou Merry! Yuki ni Kemuru Wakare no Umi
episodes.plot: The crew must finally say goodbye to their ship merry.

episodes.title: Yaburareta Ansoku! Ai no Kobushi o Motsu Kaigun Chuujou
episodes.plot: Upon their return from Enies Lobby, the Straw Hats rest in Water 7, where their new ship is being built by Franky and the Galley-La Company. Suddenly, they are attacked by Marine Vice-Admiral Garp, whom Luffy calls Grandpa.

episodes.title: Saikyou no Kakei? Akasareta Luffy no Chichi!
episodes.plot: Revelations continue as Garp sheds light on Luffy's early childhood, the whereabouts of Shanks, and the identity of Luffy's father, Monkey D. Dragon. Meanwhile, two young marines, under the Vice-Admiral's command, have a joyful reunion with members of the Straw Hats.

episodes.title: Sono Na wa Shinsekai! Grand Line no Yukue
episodes.plot: While everybody is busy celebrating their huge victory at Enies Lobby, Robin is confronted by Aokiji.

episodes.title: Shanks Ugoku! Bousou Suru Jidai e no Kusabi
episodes.plot: Shanks meets up with Whitebeard despite all the efforts made by the World Government to avoid it. His main reason for the meeting: a request to stop Ace from chasing after his former-crew mate Blackbeard.

episodes.title: Yagara o Sagasu Shoujo! Mizu no Miyako Daisousasen
episodes.plot: While walking around Water 7, Luffy and Chopper meet a young girl named Abi, who's searching for her pet Aobire that has been missing during the Aqua Laguna incident.

episodes.title: Haha wa Tsuyoshi! Zoro no Dotabata Kaji Tetsudai
episodes.plot: After being denied from various Sword Shops to get Yubashiri repaired, Zoro is tricked into becoming the new "Big Brother" to the Family of Aunt.

episodes.title: Sanji Shougeki! Nazo no Jii-san to Gekiuma Ryouri
episodes.plot: While out shopping with Chimney, Sanji is persuaded by her to go to a good cook, whom she calls grandpa. The old man teaches Sanji the reason why his food tastes so good, salt which is produced by the Aqua Laguna.

episodes.title: Tsui ni Zen'in Shoukin Kubi! 6-okugoe no Ichimi!
episodes.plot: While Usopp plots to get back in the Straw Hat Pirates, Franky, Iceburg and the Galley-La foremen are hard at work putting the finishing touches on the new ship.

episodes.title: Umi o Nozomu Hyakujuu no Ou! Yume no Fune Doudou Kansei!
episodes.plot: Soon after Sanji, Nami, and Chopper complain and object their new bounties, the Straw Hat Pirates depart to see Iceburg and their new ship.

episodes.title: Saraba Itoshiki Kobun-tachi! Franky Tatsu
episodes.plot: Franky has chased his swim briefs to the Straw Hats' new ship , but still refuses to go with them, necessitating some extra..."persuasion" from Robin and Iceburg .

episodes.title: Shukkou Mizu no Miyako! Otoko Usopp Kettou no Kejime
episodes.plot: The departure of the Straw Hats from Water 7 is hastened when Vice Admiral Garp, under watch from Aokiji, comes to attack them. Usopp has to do some soul-searching to realize what he really needs to do to rejoin the crew.

episodes.title: Meguru Tehaisho! Kokyou wa Odoru Fune wa Susumu!
episodes.plot: The Thousand Sunny finally gets its name and the Straw Hat Pirates make their getaway from Vice Admiral Garp as their hometowns get word of their new bounties.

episodes.title: Saikyou no Nouryoku! Ace o Osou Kurohige no Yami
episodes.plot: Three days before Luffy left Water 7, Ace finally catches up to Blackbeard on Banaro Island, but his attempt to fight him reveals Teach's darkest secret: the control of the Yami Yami no Mi, said to be the most evil of the Devil Fruits.

episodes.title: Nazo no Kaizoku Goikkou! Sunny-gou to Kiken na Wana
episodes.plot: After departing Water 7, the Straw Hats find a lone ship, badly damaged with no sail and flag. They decide to approach to check if everything is all right.

episodes.title: Sunny-gou Pinch! Unare Chousoku no Himitsu Mecha
episodes.plot: The Straw Hats find themselves surrounded by a fleet of Marine ships, which is actually a trap. They escape using the Soldier Dock System, with the tattered pirate ship in tow.

episodes.title: Shinsekai ni Shizumu Yume! Shitsui no Kaizoku Puzzle
episodes.plot: Trapped by moving icebergs, the Straw Hats try to figure a way out avoiding numerous dangers as the Bounty Hunters draw closer. The captain of the Phoenix Pirates, Puzzle awakens after Chopper's treatment.

episodes.title: Osoikuru Shikaku-tachi! Hyoujou Dai Battle Kaishi
episodes.plot: Using the Shark Submerge III, Nami and Franky find out that penguins are moving the icebergs. Afterwards, they are attacked by Hockera. Usopp and Sanji are knocked off the Thousand Sunny by an iceberg,

episodes.title: Dai Kusen Mugiwara Ichimi! Hata ni Kakeru Kaizoku Tamashii
episodes.plot: The fights continue with Luffy, distracted due to the lost flag, has initial trouble with Brindo, but the Phoenix Pirates help capture him.

episodes.title: Atsukurushisa Zenkai! Semaru Futago no Jiryoku Power
episodes.plot: The fight against the Accino brothers continues while Zoro accidentally arrives to Lovely Land and meets Papa.

episodes.title: Dai Konran no Yakata! Ikaru Don to Toraware no Ichimi
episodes.plot: Zoro, Nami, Sanji, Usopp and Franky gather in the ice cell where the Accino brothers left them. Robin manages Lil to get them coke and Franky sets them free. Luffy and Chopper head to Lovely land.

episodes.title: Fushichou Futatabi! Tomo ni Chikau Kaizokuki no Yume
episodes.plot: The crew decides to fool Luffy so they can recover the flag. Robin and Zoro go for it but Robin gets into trouble, while the Accino family is defeated. Don Accino goes mad when he sees his children beaten.

episodes.title: Atsu Atsu Choukessen! Luffy VS Shakunetsu no Don
episodes.plot: The crew goes into the mansion to get the flag back while Luffy finds a way to fight Don Accino. Robin gives Lil hope.

episodes.title: Shin Sekai de Matsu! Isamashiki Kaizoku to no Wakare
episodes.plot: Luffy defeats Don Accino while the crew succeeds in the restoring of the flag before Luffy notices. Campaccino comes for revenge and the Straw Hat pirates farewell the Phoenix.

episodes.title: Shutsudou Chopperman! Mamore Nagisa no TV-kyoku
episodes.plot: The adventures of Chopperman the hero and his battle against evil Usodabada.
